data.description: Welcome to this charming home located in Pembroke Pines. This property offers comfort and functionality. NEW ROOF in 2023, NO HOA, ceramic floors, Whole House Water Filter System and additional REVERSE OSMOSIS in the kitchen. It has a spacious terrace with an outdoor kitchen and a side driveway perfect for parking your RV or boats.   The location is perfect, with banks, gas stations, and markets just steps away. A spacious private yard surrounded by a NEW METAL FENCE. There is also additional space for a pool and BBQ. This property offers endless potential for those looking to customize their home.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home. Contact us today to schedule a visit!
